57,000 for the year ended January 31, against the previous deficit of Pounds
4.67m.
Net interest charges were cut by Pounds 1m to Pounds 1.24m as bank
borrowings fell from Pounds 6.1m to Pounds 4.6m by the year-end.
Earnings were 1.4p per share (losses 29.7p). The dividend is again 2.7p with
