directors' waivers totalling Pounds 334,000.
Turnover for the year rose to Pounds 56.68m (Pounds 53.31m). That generated
an operating profit of Pounds 1.3m (loss Pounds 4.19m), struck after losses
of Pounds 410,000 (Pounds 1.16m) in the US and Pounds 710,000 (Pounds
50,000) in France.
