FT  16 APR 91 / UK Company News: Asda Prop declines to Pounds 1.4m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
LOWER HOUSE prices, high interest rates and a lack of new trading
opportunities in 1990 depressed pre-tax profits at Asda Property Holdings -
they fell from Pounds 5.25m to Pounds 1.4m in the year to December 31.
Mr Manny Davidson, chairman, said that in his 40 years in the property
