FT  15 APR 91 / UK Company News: Tyndall approach
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Jupiter Tarbutt Merlin, the fund management group, is understood to have
made a bid approach to Tyndall, the quoted financial services company, after
picking up a 2.9 per cent stake.
